short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Puts you back on the homepage of Skyward whenever you are logged out.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: If your school has skyward set up to login using google and it doesn't open in a new window, then this extension will automatically place you back to the login page of skyward after it logs you out!
